Tanysa ~ Feature 02 — Spinlock verification, `sensor.c` simulation process 
Violetta ~ Feature 04 — `setsensordata` / `getsensordata` syscalls, `monitor.c`, `envtest.c` 
Rohan ~ Feature 03 — Environment-aware scheduler in `kernel/proc.c` 
All ~ Feature 05 — Persistent logger, end-to-end integration, documentation 
